  <brief_title>Randomized Trial of a Liberal Versus a Restrictive Transfusion Strategy in Elderly Cardiac Surgery Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a Liberal Versus Restrictive Blood Transfusion Strategy in Elderly Patients Following Coronary Bypass or Aortic Valve Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
